name: License Cache Status
description:
License Cache Status:
ACTIVE
STALE - when license cache record is replaced by a new record (by pulling/requesting new license data)
UNKNOWN- when the server is not responding (after n retries) and if license data has been tampered with

name: Localization Processing Result
description:
This list contains the status of the payment template request.

Passed – This status indicates that the payment file template request is successful.

Failed – This status is displayed when the payment file template request has not been generated successfully due to errors encountered while processing.

name: EP Output File Encoding
description: Based on NetSuite's accepted encoding for a file

name: Payment Mode
description: Used to source the payment mode values i.e. In-transit and Simple.

name: Environment types
description: Types of environments used for the implementation and testing of functionalities for a given engagement.

name: Change Log Change Type
description: This list is used in the Change Log in the Change Type field.

description: This list is used on the Change Log record in the Decision field.
